Package com.catan.model

Klasse VertexCoordinate

java.lang.Object
com.catan.model.VertexCoordinate
public class VertexCoordinate extends Object
Represents a vertex coordinate in the hexagonal CATAN board. Vertices are the intersections where buildings (settlements/cities) can be placed. In a hexagonal grid, each vertex is shared by 2-3 hexagon tiles.
